\c 11
\nb
\v 1 Lami-ke, ngomnyaka wokuqala\x + 9.1.\x* kaDariyusi umMede\x + 9.1.\x*, ngema uku\add m\add*qinisa lokumvikela.
\s Inkosi yenyakatho leyaseningizimu
\p
\v 2 Khathesi sengizakutshela iqiniso\x + 10.21.\x*. Khangela, kusezakuma amakhosi amathathu ePerisiya\x + 8.21.\x*; njalo eyesine izanotha ngenotho enkulu okwedlula wonke. Kuthi isiqinile ngenotho yayo ibavuse bonke bamelane lombuso weGirisi.
\v 3 Kuzasukuma-ke inkosi elamandla, ezabusa ngokubusa okukhulu\x + 7.6; 8.5,21.\x*, yenze ngokwentando yayo\x + 11.16,36; 8.4.\x*.
\v 4 Lalapho isukuma, umbuso wayo uzaqanyulwa\x + 8.8,22.\x*, wehlukaniswe ngasemimoyeni\x + 8.8,22.\x* emine yamazulu\x + 7.2.\x*; kodwa ungabi ngowenzalo yayo, ungabi njengombuso ebiwubusa\x + Hlab. 109.13; Amos 4.2.\x*; ngoba umbuso wayo uzasitshunwa, ube ngowabanye ngaphandle kwalaba.
\p
\v 5 Lenkosi yeningizimu izakuba lamandla, l\add omunye\add* weziphathamandla zayo; \add yena\add*-ke uzakuba lamandla kulayo, abuse; umbuso wakhe uzakuba ngumbuso omkhulu.
\v 6 Lekupheleni kweminyaka bazahlangana, ngoba indodakazi yombusi weningizimu izakuza kumbusi wenyakatho uku\add za\add*kwenza isivumelwano esilinganayo, kodwa kayiyikugcina amandla engalo\x + 10.8.\x*; futhi kayiyikuma, layo ingalo yakhe; kodwa izanikelwa, labayilethileyo\x + Josh. 15.18; Hlu. 1.14.\x*, loyizeleyo, loyiqinisileyo ngalezizikhathi.
\v 7 Kodwa kuzasukuma ogatsheni lwempande zayo \add e\add*sikhundl\add eni\add* sakhe, ozabuya lebutho, angene enqabeni yenkosi yenyakatho\x + 11.7,19,31,38,39.\x*, enze emelene labo, ehlule.
\v 8 Labonkulunkulu babo kanye leziphathamandla\x + Josh. 13.21.\x* zabo kanye lezitsha zabo eziloyisekayo ezesiliva legolide uzakuletha eGibhithe ekuthunjweni; yena-ke uzakuma okweminyaka kulenkosi yenyakatho.
\v 9 Ngokunjalo inkosi yeningizimu izangena embusweni, ibuyele elizweni layo.
\p
\v 10 Kodwa amadodana ayo azadungeka, ahlanganise ixuku lamabutho amakhulu\x + 11.25; Zaga 28.4.\x*; ngeqiniso kufike \add omunye\add*, agabhe\x + 11.40; Isa. 8.8; Nah. 1.8. Dan. 11.22,26; 9.26.\x*, adabule\x + 11.40; Isa. 8.8; Nah. 1.8. Dan. 11.22,26; 9.26.\x*; abuyele, adungeke, kuze kube senqabeni yakhe\x + 11.7,19,31,38,39.\x*.
\v 11 Lenkosi yeningizimu izathukuthela kakhulu\x + 8.7.\x*, iphume ilwe layo, lenkosi yenyakatho; yona izavusa ixuku elikhulu\x + 11.13.\x*, kodwa lelixuku lizanikelwa esandleni sayo.
\v 12 Selisusiwe lelixuku, inhliziyo yayo izaziphakamisa, iwisele phansi izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi \add amanengi\add*, kodwa kayiyikuba lamandla.
\v 13 Ngoba inkosi yenyakatho izaphenduka, ivuse ixuku elikhulu kulelokuqala\x + 11.13.\x*; njalo ekupheleni kwezikhathi zeminyaka izafika isibili ilebutho elikhulu lempahla ezinengi.
\p
\v 14 Langalezozikhathi abanengi bazasukuma bemelane lenkosi yeningizimu. Labalesihluku babantu bakho bazaziphakamisa\x + Hez. 18.10; 7.22.\x* ukuze bawuqinise umbono\x + Hez. 18.10; 7.22.\x*, kodwa bazakhubeka\x + 11.19; 11.33,34,41.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho inkosi yenyakatho izafika, ibuthelele idundulu\x + Hez. 4.2.\x*, ithumbe imizi ebiyelweyo. Futhi izingalo zeningizimu kaziyikuma, kanye labakhethiweyo bakhe, futhi kakuyikuba lamandla okuma.
\v 16 Kodwa eza uku\add za\add*melana layo izakwenza ngokwentando yayo\x + 11.16,36; 8.4.\x*, engekho ongema phambi kwayo\x + Josh. 10.8.\x*. Izakuma lelizweni elihle, lokutshabalaliswa kuzakuba sesandleni sayo.
\v 17 Njalo izamisa ubuso bayo ukungena ngamandla ombuso wayo wonke\x + Jer. 42.15; 2 Lan. 20.3.\x*, labaqotho belayo, ngokunjalo izakwenza; futhi izayinika indodakazi yabafazi, ukuwuchitha; kodwa kayiyikuma, kayiyikuba ngeyayo\x + 9.26.\x*.
\v 18 Emva kwalokho izaphendulela ubuso bayo ezihlengeni, ithumbe ezinengi; kodwa isiphathamandla\x + Isa. 1.10.\x* sizakwenza ihlazo layo limphelele; ngaphandle kokuthi izabuyisela ihlazo layo kuyo\x + Hos. 12.14.\x*.
\v 19 Ibisiphendulela ubuso bayo ngasezinqabeni zelizwe lakibo\x + 11.7,19,31,38,39.\x*, kodwa izakhubeka\x + 11.19; 11.33,34,41.\x*\x + Jer. 46.6.\x* iwe\x + Jer. 46.6.\x*, njalo ingatholwa\x + Jobe 20.8; Hlab. 37.36; Hez. 26.21.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Lapho kuzasukuma esikhundleni sayo odlulisa umthelisi \add k\add*udumo lombuso; kodwa phakathi kwezinsuku ezinlutshwana uzabhujiswa, kungabi ngezintukuthelo, kungabi ngezimpi\x + Gen. 27.44; 29.20.\x*.
\v 21 Lapho kuzasukuma esikhundleni sakhe odelelekileyo, abangayikumnika udumo lombuso, kodwa ezangena ngokuthula\x + 11.24; 8.25.\x*, awubambe umbuso ngamazwi abutshelezi\x + 11.34; Hlab. 35.6.\x*.
\v 22 Lezingalo zikazamcolo\x + 11.10; Jer. 46.7.\x* zizakhukhulwa phambi kobuso bakhe, zifohlozwe; yebo, laso isiphathamandla sesivumelwano\x + 11.28,30,32.\x*.
\v 23 Langemva kokuhlangana laye uzasebenza ngenkohliso\x + 8.25.\x*; ngoba ezakwenyuka\x + 11.24; 8.25.\x*, abe lamandla elesizwe esincane\x + 8.9; 11.23.\x*.
\v 24 Uzangena ngokuthula\x + 8.24; 8.25.\x* laphezu kwezindawo ezivunde kakhulu zesabelo\x + Gen. 27.28,39; Isa. 10.16.\x*; enze lokho oyise loba oyise baboyise abangakwenzanga; uzahlakaza phakathi kwabo impango lokuthunjiweyo lempahla; acebe amacebo akhe emelene lezinqaba, kodwa kuze kube yisikhathi\x + 11.15.\x*.
\v 25 Futhi uzavusa amandla akhe lenhliziyo yakhe emelene lenkosi yeningizimu elebutho elikhulu\x + 8.9.\x*; njalo inkosi yeningizimu izadungeka ilebutho elikhulu elilamandla amakhulu\x + 11.10.\x*; kodwa kayiyikuma, ngoba bazaceba amacebo bemelene layo.
\v 26 Yebo, labo abadla isabelo sokudla sayo bazayibhubhisa\x + 1.5.\x*, lebutho layo lizakhukhula\x + 11.10; Jer. 46.7.\x*, labanengi bazakuwa bebulewe.
\v 27 Njalo inhliziyo zalamakhosi amabili zikukho okubi, njalo azakhuluma amanga etafuleni elilodwa; kodwa kakuyikuphumelela, ngoba isiphetho sisezakuba khona ngesikhathi esimisiweyo\x + 11.35; 11.29,40; 8.19.\x*.
\v 28 Lapho ezabuyela \add e\add*lizw\add eni\add* lakhe elempahla ezinengi; kodwa inhliziyo yakhe izamelana\x + 11.30; 7.21; 8.10.\x* lesivumelwano esingcwele\x + 11.22.\x*; njalo uzakwenza, abesebuyela elizweni lakhe\x + 11.30; 8.12; 11.32.\x*.
\p
\v 29 Ngesikhathi esimisiweyo uzaphenduka, eze ngaseningizimu\x + 11.35; 11.29,40; 8.19.\x*; kodwa kakuyikuba njengokwakuqala loba njengokokucina\x + 11.23-25.\x*.
\v 30 Ngoba imikhumbi yeKitimi izakuza imelane laye\x + Nani 24.24; Gen. 10.4.\x*; ngakho uzadabuka, abuyele emuva, athukuthelele\x + 11.30; 7.21; 8.10.\x* isivumelwano esingcwele\x + 11.22.\x*; njalo uzakwenza\x + 11.30; 8.12; 11.32.\x*, abesebuyela, anakane labo abadele isivumelwano esingcwele\x + 11.22.\x*.
\v 31 Lezingalo zizakuma zivela kuye, zingcolise indawo engcwele \add ey\add*inqaba, asuse \add umnikelo\add* oqhubekayo\x + 12.11; 8.11.\x*, amise isinengiso esichithayo\x + Mat. 24.15; Dan. 9.27.\x*.
\v 32 Lalabo abenza inkohlakalo bemelene lesivumelwano uzabangcolisa\x + Nani 35.33; Jer. 3.2.\x* ngamazwi abutshelezi\x + 11.21.\x*; kodwa abantu abamaziyo uNkulunkulu wabo bazaqina, benze.
\v 33 Njalo abaqedisisayo babantu bazafundisa abanengi\x + 11.35; 12.3,10.\x*; kanti\x + Heb. 11.35-38.\x* bazakuwa ngenkemba\x + 11.14.\x*, langelangabi, ngokuthunjwa, langokuphangwa, izinsuku \add ezinengi\add*.
\v 34 Kuzakuthi lapho besiwa\x + 11.14.\x*, basizwe\x + Luka 1.54.\x* ngosizo oluncinyane, kodwa abanengi bazazihlanganisa labo ngamazwi abutshelezi\x + 11.21.\x*.
\v 35 Kodwa \add abanye\add* kwabaqedisisayo\x + 11.35; 12.3,10.\x* bazakuwa\x + 11.14.\x*, ukubalinga\x + 12.10; Zek. 13.9; 1 Pet. 1.7.\x*, loku\add ba\add*hlambulula\x + 12.10; Zek. 13.9; 1 Pet. 1.7.\x*\x + Tshu. 3.18; Mal. 3.2,3.\x*, loku\add b\add*enza babe mhlophe\x + 12.10; Zek. 13.9; 1 Pet. 1.7.\x*\x + Isam. 7.14.\x*, kuze kube yisikhathi sokuphela\x + 11.40; 8.17.\x*; ngoba kusezakuba ngokwesikhathi esimisiweyo\x + 11.27.\x*.
