\v 36 Njalo inkosi izakwenza njengokwentando yayo\x + 11.3.\x*, iziphakamise\x + 2 Thes. 2.4; Isam. 13.5,6; Dan. 7.25.\x*, izikhulise ngaphezu kwabo bonke onkulunkulu\x + 11.37; 8.11.\x*, ikhulume izinto ezimangalisayo\x + 11.21.\x* imelene loNkulunkulu wabonkulunkulu\x + Dute. 10.17.\x*, iphumelele\x + 8.12.\x* kuze kuphelele\x + 9.27.\x* intukuthelo\x + Isa. 10.25; 8.19.\x*; ngoba lokho okumisiweyo kuzakwenziwa\x + 9.27.\x*.
\v 37 Futhi kayiyikunaka onkulunkulu baboyise, lesiloyiso sabesifazana\x + 1 Tim. 4.3; Hag. 2.7.\x*, njalo kayiyikunaka loba nguwuphi unkulunkulu\x + 11.37; 8.11.\x*; ngoba izazikhulisa phezu kwabo bonke\x + 11.37; 8.11.\x*.
\v 38 Kodwa esikhundleni sakhe uzadumisa unkulunkulu wezinqaba, ngitsho unkulunkulu oyise ababengamazi amdumise ngegolide langesiliva\x + Isam. 17.4.\x* langamatshe aligugu\x + Isam. 17.4.\x* langezinto eziloyisekayo.
\v 39 Njalo izakwenza ezinqabeni ezilamandla ikanye lonkulunkulu wezizweni; amnanzelelayo amandisele udumo. Izabenza babuse phezu kwabanengi, yehlukanise ilizwe ngentengo.
