\v 40 Langesikhathi sokuphela inkosi yeningizimu\x + 11.35.\x* izamsunduza\x + 8.4.\x*; kodwa inkosi yenyakatho izamelana layo njengesivunguzane\x + Zek. 9.14.\x*, ilezinqola\x + Hez. 38.4,15; Isam. 9.16.\x*, labagadi bamabhiza, lemikhumbi eminengi\x + Hez. 38.4,15; Isam. 9.16.\x*; ingene emazweni, ikhukhule\x + 11.10.\x*, idlule\x + 11.10.\x*.
\v 41 Njalo izangena elizweni elihle, njalo \add amazwe\add* amanengi azakuwa\x + 11.14.\x*; kodwa la azaphunyuka esandleni sakhe\x + 12.1.\x*, iEdoma\x + 11.14.\x* loMowabi\x + 11.14.\x* lekhethelo labantwana bakoAmoni\x + 11.14.\x*.
